1277
01:03:29,292 --> 01:03:30,082
Xin lỗi!

1278
01:03:52,822 --> 01:03:53,321
Nào!

1279
01:03:55,450 --> 01:03:56,150
Từ từ.

1280
01:03:59,049 --> 01:03:59,819
